1. User/Key based authentication
	-	VPC, EC2
	- Groups  
		- Devops Engineer
			- Read only on all files
		- Devops Admin
			- Full access on the node including its contents and applications
		- App user
			- Read only on a need basis
2. Elastic Load balancer and Application Load balancer
3. Security aspects
	-	Closure of unwanted ports
	-	Policy of Least privilege
4. High Availability and Fault tolerance
		
